behavior.description:
Tune how the cover behaves once a position is chosen: sunset/sunrise timing adjustments, the position-match tolerance and matching toggle, and inverse-state. These are not target positions — every percentage value lives on the Position Settings step; this step holds only the timing and threshold knobs.

[Learn more]({learn_more})

{profile_inherit}

weather_override.description:
Configure weather-based safety overrides. Any configured condition triggers cover retraction. Unconfigured inputs are ignored.

[Learn more]({learn_more})

{profile_inherit}

debug.description:
Enable debug mode to collect detailed troubleshooting data without editing configuration.yaml. When active, selected categories are logged at INFO level and a diagnostic event ring buffer is kept in memory and exposed in the HA Diagnostics download.

{cover_capabilities}

[Learn more]({learn_more})

